    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink424-kilavi">ituvum atu</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">And this is that.</p>
            </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <lg xml:id="Aink424">        
            <l>puṟavaṇi nāṭaṉ kātaṉ maṭamaka</l>
            <l>ḷoṇṇutal pacappa nīceliṟ ṟeṇṇīrp</l>
            <l>pōtaviḻ tāmarai yaṉṉaniṉ</l>
            <l>kātalam putalva ṉaḻumiṉi mulaikkē.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that the bright forehead of the beloved naive daughter becomes pale</l>
<l>of the man from the land adorned with forests, if you go,</l>
<l>your loving son, who is like a lotus with opening buds in the clear water,</l>
<l>O lord, will start criyng for her breast.<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">As I understand it, the son will be crying out for his mother's breast becasue she, on account of being stricken wiht lovesickness, will be unable to care for him. Whether this implies that she will be so physically weak that she grows unable to nurse, or that she is unable to provide him emotional care, I am not sure.</note></l>
          </lg>

        </div>
      </body>
    </text>
